{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_176","type":"agent_message","text":"The new probe showed something important: the failure isn’t isolated to a YAML class. Groovy’s `checkCanSetAccessible` is null-crashing even on plain `java.lang.Object` methods during meta-class bootstrap, which is why the failure reproduces before the tests even instantiate. I’m checking whether the repo already handles this elsewhere for other Groovy artifacts before deciding whether a metadata-only fix is still viable."}}
